                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40108055/" class="">第6页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fayolee/" class=" " title="看不见的城市">看不见的城市</a>
                (Aedificabo et destruam)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40108055">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">胖乎乎的休谟毫无嫉妒之心，善于交际，乐观宽厚。似乎只有他广受欢迎，是启蒙哲人家族中受宠爱的小舅舅。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40108055/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
